We know that this is going to require a lot more calls to action.

00:03:50.720 --> 00:03:55.480
But this needs to be done to protect content on the internet. All of our content.

00:03:55.500 --> 00:03:59.740
Whether you're trying to just to upload pictures or entertain someone- we're all at risk.

00:03:59.740 --> 00:04:02.920
